overview.en: Pet chain PETT is based on blockchain and smart contract technology, It is committed to building the pet ecosystem of the next generation of AI + IoT + blockchain, incubating the sharing economy, and generating quantitative value for users' network behavior and idle resources.
overview.zh: 宠物链PETT是基于区块链及智能合约技术，致力于打造下一代人工智能+物联网+区块 链的宠物生态，孵化共享经济，让用户网络行为及闲置资源产生量化价值。
